\v 14 \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w then|strong="G2532"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* snake \w came|strong="G1096"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* trick \w them|strong="G3588"\w*, \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* didn’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* trick Adam. \w He|strong="G2532"\w* tricked Eve, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w she|strong="G2532"\w* \w went|strong="G2532"\w* wrong \w first|strong="G3588"\w*.\x * \xo 2:14 \xt Genesis 3:1-6\x*
